			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "select player character\r\nin reCon: addTag BARBARIAN\r\nteleport S_DEN_CharmedKid\r\ntrigger dialogue DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim\r\ngo through these choices\r\n- You shouldn't be standing out in the water. It's dangerous.\r\n-  Focus and try to hear what he hears.\r\n-  Struggle against the music's pull. (roll amazing)\r\n- Roar at the top of your lungs to overpower the voice.\r\ndialogue exits\r\nkillcombat\r\nclick through next dialogue (spacebar all the way)\r\noe startdruidattack\r\nteleport S_DEN_CharmedKid"
				},
